                  <note>arranged for the days of the week. This version of the Praises of Mary is unique in that the catchword for each day is repeated throughout the text for the day. For instance, on Monday the catchword is <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሠረቀ</foreign>, and it appears at the head of each sub-section within the Monday reading</note>
